	@echo	"⠀⠀⠀⢀⡤⠖⠋⠁⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀$(YELLOW)⢀⣶⣶⣦ $(GREEN)⠈⠻⠻⣆⠀⠀⠀ ⠀$(YELLOW)⠀⢸⢸⣿⣿⣿⣟⣴⣦⣻⣿⣿⣿⡇⡇$(GREEN)⠀⠀⠀"
